scenes.description: Vestia Zeta provides details and information about her birthday merchandise and voice packs.
A transition scene featuring a vintage television set.
Narration introducing the story of 'Alice in Musicland'.
Vestia Zeta performs the song 'Alice in Musicland' on a storybook-style stage, joined by Kobo Kanaeru as the White Rabbit.

subtitles.original: 昔話より
subtitles.english: even better than old tales,

subtitles.original: もっともっと素敵な
subtitles.english: a much, much more wonderful

subtitles.original: お伽話
subtitles.english: fairy tale.

subtitles.original: 扉を開けると
subtitles.english: When I open the door,

subtitles.original: 真っ白なうさぎ
subtitles.english: there's a pure white rabbit.

subtitles.english: I'll follow behind.

subtitles.original: チクタク チクタク 急いで行かなきゃ間に合わない
subtitles.english: Tick-tock, tick-tock, I have to hurry or I won't make it!

subtitles.original: あぁ チクタク チクタク ぎくしゃくするのはもう嫌だ
subtitles.english: Ah, tick-tock, tick-tock, I hate being so flustered.

subtitles.original: そら チクタク チクタク 時間はどんどん減ってゆく
subtitles.english: Look, tick-tock, tick-tock, the time keeps ticking away.

subtitles.original: もう とにかく僕には時間がない
subtitles.english: Goodness, anyway, I just don't have any time!

subtitles.original: ねぇ そんなに慌てて一体全体どうしたの？
subtitles.english: Hey, what in the world happened for you to be in such a hurry?

subtitles.original: どこかの誰かといつかどこかで待ち合わせ？
subtitles.english: Are you meeting someone somewhere at some time?

subtitles.original: そう 彼女はチクタクとっても時間にシビアだよ
subtitles.english: Yes, she is tick-tock, very strict about time.

subtitles.original: そんなに？
subtitles.english: That much?

subtitles.original: そうさ！
subtitles.english: Exactly!

subtitles.original: だって彼女は女王様
subtitles.english: Because she is the Queen.
